The 7th Hatfield Cubs "Every Tuesday at 6.30p.m. Steven and I go to Cubs. We have 4 groups in our pack called Brown, Green, Blue and Yellow. We are both sixers, which means we are leaders of our groups. We have both been at Cubs for nearly 3 years and have got our Bronze and Silver Arrow Awards. We are now working for our Gold.
